title: Check out my custom Masked Shaco design on Photoshop!
body:
I know I'm not a god of Photoshop, but I thought I'd just show you guys a quick fan art of your favourite demon jester.
I decided to change the mask all together, thought it turned out pretty cool :')
In case you haven't noticed, I have a huge love for {{champion:35}}  (my username speaks for itself) :')

Edit: I have no idea why but if I upload a single photo of it, it won't enlarge so I uploaded two copies and the second one becomes enlarged!

replies.body:
Picture can not be enlarged.

"This image failed to load".
Uploaded a second one, it should enlarge now :)
